These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: indie, jazz, trance, pop, funk
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: crime, family, satire, western, zombie
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: december, march, november, july, june
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, black, apricot, orange, turquise
 1. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
 2. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
 3. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person who likes red##1
 4. the fan of trance is the fan of trance##1
 5. the person who likes red is the person watching crime movies##1
 6. the fan of funk is on the left of the fan of trance##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 8. the fan of pop is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
 9. the fan of pop is on the far right##1
10. the fan of indie is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
11. the fan of funk is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person watching zombie movies##2
12. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
13. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Music-Genre      | indie        | jazz | funk     | trance   | pop |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | family      | western | zombie   | crime    |
| Birthday   | july  | march     | december | november | june  |
| Color           | black | apricot      | turquise     | orange   | red     |

