.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
House: art-deco, tower, townhouse, craftsman, farmhouse
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, d&b, disco, r&b, techno
The people have 5 different jobs:  writer, software-developer, photographer, chef, bartender
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, aristoff, pall-mall, cain, tiparillo
 1. the tiparillo-smoker is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of techno is on the left of the art-deco house##1
 3. the tower house is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 4. the farmhouse house is on the right of the software-developer##1
 5. the aristoff-smoker is between the writer and the fan of techno##2
 6. the cain-smoker is the tower house##1
 7. the fan of country is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
 8. the photographer is the fan of r&b##1
 9. the photographer is on the right of the tower house##1
10. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
11. the photographer is the townhouse house##1
12. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the bartender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| House         | craftsman | art-deco | farmhouse    | tower  | townhouse    |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | d&b       | disco      | country | r&b        |
| Job   | bartender   | software-developer     | writer    | chef  | photographer     |
| Cigar     | pall-mall    | aristoff | tiparillo | cain | bongani |

