.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: coral, amber, blue, emerald, aquamarine
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, documentary, family, martial-arts, superhero
5 different games are played: monopoly, billiard, canasta, domino, bridge
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, zinnia, rose, daisy, orchid
 1. the person who likes aquamarine is the person playing billiard##1
 2. the person who growsdaisy is in the middle##1
 3. the person playing domino is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
 5. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 6. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 7. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 9. the person playing canasta is on the far left##1
10. the person who growsamaryllis is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
11. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
12. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
13. the person who growsorchid is between the person watching superhero movies and the person who likes blue##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Color         | coral | aquamarine     | blue   | amber   | emerald |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero  | documentary | adventure | martial-arts | family        |
