 1. the egyptian is on the far left##1
 2. the coach is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
 3. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 4. the pakistani is between the old-henry-smoker and the owner of the rabbit##2
 5. the owner of the goat is on the right of the dancer##1
 6. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the indonesian##1
 7. the dancer is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 8. the project-manager is the vegafina-smoker##1
 9. the ritmeester-smoker is in the middle##1
10. the old-henry-smoker is the british##1
11. the lawyer is on the right of the dancer##1
12. the british is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
13. the vegafina-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Pet          | turtle  | fish     | rabbit   | goat     | pony |
