 1. the person who growsiris is in the middle##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
 3. the fan of house is on the far right##1
 4. the person drinking water is the person who growsdahlia##1
 5. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
 7. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 8. the person drinking cola is the fan of dubstep##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
10. the fan of rock is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
11. the fan of r&b is between the person drinking cola and the person who's birthday is in june##2
12. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
13. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
