.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
House: victorian, ranch-style, farmhouse, art-deco, craftsman
The people have 5 different hobbies: card-games, drawing, reading, traveling, video-games
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: azalea, zinnia, tulip, marigold, iris
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, rock, country, soul, reggae
 1. the person who growsiris is between the fan of rock and the person who growszinnia##2
 2. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
 3. the ranch-style house is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 4. the victorian house is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
 5. the fan of rock is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the fan of rock##1
 7. the fan of blues is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 9. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
10. the person who growstulip is on the far left##1
11. the fan of country is between the person who growstulip and the person who's hobby is reading##2
12. the art-deco house is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
13. the farmhouse house is on the left of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
