 2. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who growsdaffodil##2
 3. the person playing canasta is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the fan of house##1
 5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in the middle##1
 6. the person playing canasta is between the person who growsdahlia and the fan of blues##2
 7. the fan of house is the person playing monopoly##1
 8. the person playing domino is the fan of hip-hop##1
 9. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
10. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
11. the person who growsdaffodil is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
12. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left##1
13. the person playing go is on the far right##1

