.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: lacrosse, sailing, cycling, golf, skateboarding
City: edinburgh, berlin, paris, san-francisco, rome
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: january, august, may, july, december
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, car, helicopter, jet-ski, ship
 1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
 3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person who's birthday is in january##2
 6. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's sport is cycling is between the person driving the airplane and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
 8. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
10. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| Sport         | skateboarding  | cycling | golf   | sailing      | lacrosse |
| City   | edinburgh   | san-francisco    | berlin | rome | paris      |
| Birthday           | may | august    | january       | july     | december      |
| Transport     | helicopter | ship        | airplane  | car        | jet-ski    |

