.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: tram, roller, snowmobile, subway, scooter
5 different games are played: monopoly, mah-jongg, billiard, domino, backgammon
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: tulip, lily, daffodil, amaryllis, zinnia
There are 5 different nationalities: american, australian, egyptian, malaysian, thai
 1. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 2. the person playing backgammon is between the malaysian and the person who growszinnia##2
 3. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
 4. the person playing backgammon is the person who growstulip##1
 5. the person who growstulip is between the thai and the person who growsdaffodil##2
 6. the thai is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
 7. the person playing billiard is the person who growsamaryllis##1
 8. the person driving the subway is the person who growslily##1
 9. the american is the person who growslily##1
10. the person driving the subway is on the right of the egyptian##1
11. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
12. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Transport         | snowmobile    | scooter  | roller  | tram      | subway |
| Game   | mah-jongg    | backgammon   | domino | billiard | monopoly   |
| Flower   | daffodil | tulip    | zinnia    | amaryllis       | lily         |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | australian | thai    | egyptian     | american      |

 